The Oblitercons/Double Punch/Manterror/Demon Wulf/Dark Claw/Flesh Ripper/
Injector/Bumblebee/Sixshot/Ares:



Both shuttles touched down, Injector, Bumblebee, Sixshot, Ares, Dark One, and 
Hiss already waiting for their comrades.

Out poured the rest of the Oblitercons, Pyro transforming into his tank mode, 
Breakdown climbing in, Scavenger transforming to his HUMV mode, the 
Oblitercons heading for Vehement's base.

The rest of the robots headed for the platform, the shuttles flying back 
towards the Iron Fist.
